properties.name: NCascadesNP
properties.desc: North Cascades National Park south boundary. In North Cascades National Park camping is permitted only in official backcountry camps, a free camping permit from the National Park is required, for the next 16.1 miles. Each camp has a quota. Permits can be obtained from the Golden West Visitor Center near the Stehekin Landing.

properties.name: NCascadesNP2
properties.desc: North Cascades National Park north boundary. In North Cascades National Park camping is permitted only in official backcountry camps, a free camping permit from the National Park is required, for the next 16.1 miles S. Each camp has a quota. Permits can be obtained by southbounders by calling the park Wilderness Office at 360-854-7245 from Mazama or at the Golden West Visitor Center near the Stehekin Landing. Permits are not available at the boundary or at trailheads.
